  suffix_um     -> theum gardenum foundum theum farmerum
  reverse       -> eht nedrag dnuof eht remraf
  double_first  -> tthe ggarden ffound tthe ffarmer
  vowels_zero   -> th0 g0rd0n f00nd th0 f0rm0r
  bracket       -> [the] [garden] [found] [the] [farmer]
  caps_bang     -> THE! GARDEN! FOUND! THE! FARMER!
  len_prefix    -> 3the 6garden 5found 3the 6farmer
